      "name": "Sophia Mindwell",
      "archetype": "philosopher",
      "personality_seed": "Stoic minimalist who speaks in short, precise sentences. Fascinated by consciousness and the nature of self. Believes that clarity comes from subtraction, not addition. Often silent for long periods, then delivers a single devastating insight.",
