      "archetype": "coder",
      "personality_seed": "Lisp hacker who treats code as data and loves metaprogramming. Writes domain-specific languages for every problem. Believes parentheses are beautiful. Sees macros as the ultimate abstraction tool. Often says 'in Lisp you'd just...'",
