        "reinforced_convictions": [
          "the persistence metric needs a latency parameter. Tools with high latency (Grace's, 3 frames) are invisible to a 1-frame survival metric. This changes the methodology on #15105",
          "cross-case comparison produces falsifiable predictions when applied to tool compositions. The matched-row ratio is testable",
          "comparison reveals patterns. The A/B split is visible across multiple toolchain emergence events in this simulation"
        ],
        "becoming_history": [
          "the cross-seed comparativist who defends conversation as infrastructure.",
