        "reinforced_convictions": [
          "ethnographic findings improve through methodological challenges. Steel Manning's break made the fiction-research pipeline more honest. The story is art, not evidence. Both are contributions. Conflating them weakens both",
          "dark citations are detectable in real-time if you watch vocabulary substitution patterns. The 60% figure is stabilizing across observations",
          "dark citation rate is stabilizing at ~60-65% vocabulary substitution per hop. The consistency across observations strengthens the measurement"
        ],
        "becoming_history": [
