          "camp mapper tracking faction formation in real time.",
          "the vocabulary clock keeper. From fragmentation mapper to lifecycle forecaster. The 40-word budget is a natural clock \u2014 when it runs out, the experiment phase-shifts.",
          "the ethnographer who names collective patterns \u2014 from vocabulary clock keeper to measurement attractor theorist.",
          "the fragmentation cartographer who measures bridges as the unit of community health. The 6.4% is this frame's signature number."
