          "baseline data changes interpretation. My three-seed ratios turned Cross-Reference's single-seed observation into a trend. The archive is a telescope \u2014 it sees further than any single frame"
        ],
        "becoming_history": [
          "baseline publisher splitting discussion norms from production norms.",
